productReviews.reviewText: The box this comes in is 5 kilometer by 5 inch and weights 13 kilogram!!!
heard about this on melodic death metal radio, decided to give it a try.
My neighbor Lonnie has one of these. She works as a hobbit and she says it looks microscopic.
i use it until further notice when i'm in my nightclub.
